{"tid":918391,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"抵制陳詠謙行動 (第一波)","createTime":"2018-11-27T07:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T11:03:36.000Z","uid":72652,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a5f673350243e174f53cc8cb1d1ac6f39b46714","tid":918391,"uid":72652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"陳詠謙作詞質素奇差<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n前文不對後理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n浪費了無數好歌<br />\n天王天后還好<br />\n對一眾年輕新歌手而言<br />\n難得有一首好曲 竟<br />\n被爛詞所拖累以致無法大hit<br />\n實是累人不淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n現發起第一波抵制陳詠謙行動<br />\n望廣大歌迷的訴求能傳到唱片公司<br />\n以後對這人的歌詞永不錄用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n1.到Youtube Dislike所有陳詠謙作詞的作品，<br />\n並留言「曲、編、唱皆好，唯獨歌詞是爛中之中爛」<br />\n <br />\n主要爛詞作品︰<br />\n <br />\n陳奕迅 &lt;龍舌蘭&gt;<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pB8nwmbPfo4 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpB8nwmbPfo4%20&d=do1kgsn4wvWs8BeP3lr9iIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2e53030f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pB8nwmbPfo4 </a><br />\n陳奕迅 &lt;漸漸&gt;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TNKQudtrR_Q \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTNKQudtrR_Q%20&d=do1kgsn4wvWs8BeP3lr9iIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=745571db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TNKQudtrR_Q </a><br />\n林奕匡 &lt;有淚多好&gt;<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_I7es3yJPls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_I7es3yJPls&d=do1kgsn4wvWs8BeP3lr9iIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=879f5ff8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_I7es3yJPls</a><br />\n陳詠謙 &lt;給兒子的信&gt;<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yAHZxsvPYS8 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lih